&lt;p&gt;This is more than a traditional outbound role. You’ll help prospective customers rethink how work gets done, partner closely with Account Executives and Marketing, and experiment with new strategies to unlock opportunities across the customer journey. You’ll become a trusted voice for Airtable’s vision while developing the commercial and strategic skills needed for a long-term career Agentic AI software selling.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note, this is a hybrid role based in London, with an expectation of 3 days per week in the office.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
