&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Airtable is the no-code app platform that empowers people closest to the work to accelerate their most critical business processes. More than 500,000 organizations, including 80% of the Fortune 100, rely on Airtable to transform how work gets done.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Airtable has a design system with real foundations and a community of designers and engineers who contribute to it. We’re looking for someone who can be dedicated to building out and evolving this system, as well as bring a sharp point of view on how AI changes the way UI gets built. You’ll sit in Design, but your work lives equally in Figma and production code. This is a high-autonomy IC role with broad cross-functional reach.&lt;/p&gt;
