&lt;li&gt;You are able to prioritize a path forward. You have strong instincts on sequencing and know what to fix now, what to document and defer, and what to let go.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You raise the bar around you. The best version of this role doesn’t just improve the system—it improves how everyone at Airtable builds UI. You’re motivated by that multiplier effect.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
