&lt;div class=&quot;mb1&quot;&gt;This role sits at the intersection of strategy, analytics, and AI fluency. You take an idea from concept to action to results: framing the problem, building the analysis, and turning it into a clear action plan that leaders execute against. The best fit moves between a forecast model, a leadership read-out, and an AI-assisted workflow in the same afternoon&lt;/div&gt;
