&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Generate insights from pipeline, forecast, productivity, and revenue data. Synthesize findings into clear, actionable narratives for sales leadership — not just the numbers, but what they mean and what to do about them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Support the sales planning cycle end to end, including capacity modeling, territory design, quota allocation, and GTM strategy development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Drive the forecasting operating rhythm. Triangulate forecast calls with data and analytics, identify risks and upside, and help leadership sharpen accuracy over time.&lt;/li&gt;
