&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Take ambiguous, high-priority requests from across the sales org and turn them into structured plans with clear deliverables. Flex across workstreams rather than operating in a single lane.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams — Finance, Marketing, Product, and Revenue Operations — to align on shared metrics, planning inputs, and strategic priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
