&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You understand how a sales org works at a foundational level — pipeline mechanics, forecasting methodologies, territory design, and core GTM metrics are concepts you can operate on immediately, not ones you need to learn on the job.&lt;/li&gt;
