&lt;li&gt;Make technical sequencing decisions when platform constraints, compliance requirements, or partner dependencies force tradeoffs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide customers through AI workflow transformation, helping them move from human-run processes to AI-augmented and agent-assisted operations, and managing the organizational dynamics that come with it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools actively in your own delivery operations: status reporting, risk synthesis, documentation, and stakeholder communication. You don&#39;t just manage teams using AI; you use it yourself.&lt;/li&gt;
