&lt;li&gt;Coordinate compliance, security, access management, and third-party approvals in regulated enterprise environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep executive stakeholders accurately informed without requiring them to understand the technical details.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly in Airtable as an operational tool; hands-on platform fluency is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
